member.name: EMRSETICMPROFILE
member.summary: The EMRSETICMPROFILE structure contains members for the enhanced metafile record.

member.name: EMRSETICMPROFILE.emr
member.summary: The base structure for all record types.

member.name: EMRSETICMPROFILE.dwFlags
member.summary: The profile flags. This member can be SETICMPROFILE_EMBEDED (0x00000001).

member.name: EMRSETICMPROFILE.cbName
member.summary: The size of the desired profile name.

member.name: EMRSETICMPROFILE.cbData
member.summary: The size of profile data, if attached.

member.name: EMRSETICMPROFILE.Data
member.summary: An array that contains the profile data. The length of this array is cbName plus cbData.
